{"tid":863405,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英軍19萬人中3萬超重　近1.8萬軍人癡肥","createTime":"2018-10-15T14:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T06:01:32.000Z","uid":79563,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1119bdc9608a52d881a7244b03d9abf3c3f714","tid":863405,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181015/s00005/1539600173286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181015%2Fs00005%2F1539600173286&d=SzeCi%2Frp0vCg6CgE8yKKz8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=65b4e6c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181015%2Fs00005%2F1539600173286&h=3ea1bfa2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181015/s00005/1539600173286</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181015/s00005/a931225dbfb82e37ec075b8e3fefd870.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181015%2Fs00005%2Fa931225dbfb82e37ec075b8e3fefd870.jpg&h=3d30ec23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國國防部數字顯示，19萬英軍中有逾3萬人超重，另近1.8萬人癡肥。有軍官認為這些軍人在戰鬥中，會令自己及同袍身陷險境，促請當局將他們革職。<br />\n<br />\n根據國防部按照《資訊自由法》公開的數據，截至今年7月，英軍中共有近1.8萬人癡肥，即身體質量指數（BMI）超過30。當中8662人屬陸軍，4666人屬海軍，4274人則來自空軍，部分人更患上二型糖尿病，甚至要接受抽脂手術。另若以較側重身體脂肪比率的「身體組成指數」（Body Composition Measure）計算，全英19萬軍人中，有逾3萬人超重。<br />\n<br />\n曾在阿富汗擔任軍隊指揮官的上校肯普（Richard Kemp）稱，超重及癡肥軍人仍能留在部隊，只因當局未能解決軍隊人手問題，「（留着這批軍人）是昂貴和騙人的」（expensive and fraudulent）。他認為這些體型不達標的軍人，在任何戰鬥中都會令自己和身邊的同袍陷入險境，促請當局將他們革除。<br />\n<br />\n國務部表示，軍人都要通過體能測試，不合格者會獲提供減肥餐及健體支援，以恢復健康體重。<br />\n<br />\n（每日郵報/倫敦晚旗報/British Forces Network）"},{"pid":"9bfadc0f4cc7edf1039a25f886e5a523b9a01aa2","tid":863405,"uid":69213,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T14:40:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6773ed134e93e580ab82dc1e332d5